                <h3 style="margin-left:30px;">4.2	DOCUMENT CHANGES & REAPPROVAL: </h3>

                <h5 style="margin-left:50px;">4.2.1</h5>
                <p style="margin-left:70px;">
                    Whenever any changes requires in the documents, the concerned user/originator shall generate the document change note, form no.
                    FMR03 and hand over to approving authority
                </p>


                <h5 style="margin-left:50px;">4.2.2 </h5>
                <p style="margin-left:70px;">
                    Approving authority shall review the proposal and approve the same. After approval, the same shall be handed over to issuing authority.

                </p>

                <h5 style="margin-left:50px;">
                    4.2.3

                </h5>
                <p style="margin-left:70px;">
                    Issuing authority shall revise the document and gets re-approval from approving authority.

                </p>
                <h5 style="margin-left:50px;">4.2.4 </h5>
                <p style="margin-left:70px;">
                    After getting re-approval of revise document, issuing authority shall issue the revised documents and withdraw the
                    obsolete documents from the concerned person.

                </p>

                <h5 style="margin-left:50px;"> 4.2.5 </h5>
                <p style="margin-left:70px;">
                    Issuing Authority shall keep the master copy with him. Issuing authority shall keep the copy of document change note with invalid
